data.comment: Proof Of Ely; Don't Trust, Verify.
data.metadata:
{"description":"Abstract ecosystem was where I met Ely. He joined with a bang, found his jam and started Max Abstracting everyone! 

Jokes apart, Ely is not only an awesome creator but also a passionate crypto warrior. 

qualities based on my experiences with him

1. Top tier creator with market pulse - Versatile content with current focus on live streaming & videos. From interviews to walkthroughs, everything executed with top entertainment value. Understands and acts on meta.

2. Approachable & Helpful - Never felt there was a big distance when speaking with Ely. We have honest straight to the point convo always which helps moves things along much faster with better outcomes.

3. Bold - Doesn't shy away to experiement with new projects. Sometimes it can be harmful to him and his community if projects rug however he is upfront about risks involved. 

4. Top Abstract mindshare - Almost always within the top 10 on any time frame for Abstract ecosystem.

And lastly founder and host of Max Abstraction - one of the top channnels on Abstream with great guests thus far."}

translation.translatedContent: Proof Of Ely; Don't Trust, Verify.
translation.translatedDescription:
Abstract ecosystem was where I met Ely. He joined with a bang, found his jam and started Max Abstracting everyone! 

Jokes apart, Ely is not only an awesome creator but also a passionate crypto warrior. 

qualities based on my experiences with him

1. Top tier creator with market pulse - Versatile content with current focus on live streaming & videos. From interviews to walkthroughs, everything executed with top entertainment value. Understands and acts on meta.

2. Approachable & Helpful - Never felt there was a big distance when speaking with Ely. We have honest straight to the point convo always which helps moves things along much faster with better outcomes.

3. Bold - Doesn't shy away to experiement with new projects. Sometimes it can be harmful to him and his community if projects rug however he is upfront about risks involved. 

4. Top Abstract mindshare - Almost always within the top 10 on any time frame for Abstract ecosystem.

And lastly founder and host of Max Abstraction - one of the top channnels on Abstream with great guests thus far.

data.metadata: {"description":"Knew Bunya during the pre-launch of Abstractio and we got promoted to Gigachad in the same batch during the Abstractio checker launch.\n\nWhen I expected that our promotion might be too late to be included in the list of Abstractio, Bunya updated us that all newly promoted Chads are eligible. translation.translatedDescription:
I knew Bunya during the pre-launch of Abstractio, and we were both promoted to Gigachad in the same batch during the Abstractio checker launch.

When I was worried that our promotion might be too late to be included in the Abstractio list, Bunya updated us to say that all newly promoted Chads were eligible. This reflects the quality and care that Bunya, as a founder, has for the community, which made me truly admire him.
